{"tid":709116,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[威士忌11] 威士忌真係複雜多變 唔識既都入黎傾幾句","createTime":"2018-06-19T18:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T18:43:48.000Z","uid":61267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1deabec8563148f0138a1565e0546e885da0d7a1","tid":709116,"uid":61267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T18:08:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">個格式係沿用久米仙巴打開既<br />\n上個post 冇申報番唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔打算自己整一個 會將久米仙巴打 既格式改一改下</span><br />\n<br />\n完全未飲過Whisky<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔明有咩咁令人著迷既可以睇下小弟既文章：<br />\n點解唔試下威士忌？ <a href=\"https://is.gd/MsHdou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FMsHdou&d=Jgko0oAfh0uKBKLDRogm5PjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=8ae6d76d\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/MsHdou</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Basic knowledge基本野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n1. 威士忌達人的威士忌學苑 <a href=\"https://is.gd/OeByyc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FOeByyc&d=Jgko0oAfh0uKBKLDRogm5PjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=d4284135\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/OeByyc</a><br />\n2. 關於威士忌 書上沒教你的事 <a href=\"https://is.gd/M6C8VQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FM6C8VQ&d=Jgko0oAfh0uKBKLDRogm5PjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=773a6c2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/M6C8VQ</a><br />\n3. Maltmadness Beginners&rsquo;Guide <a href=\"https://is.gd/xouIeM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FxouIeM&d=Jgko0oAfh0uKBKLDRogm5PjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=b2a3f656\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/xouIeM</a><br />\n4. 關於威士忌不可不知的十件事 <a href=\"https://is.gd/ydAjAs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FydAjAs&d=Jgko0oAfh0uKBKLDRogm5PjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=bb356eec\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/ydAjAs</a><br />\n5. 漫談威士忌品酒技巧 <a href=\"https://is.gd/1O3Fvy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2F1O3Fvy&d=Jgko0oAfh0uKBKLDRogm5PjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=adbb2a23\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/1O3Fvy</a><br />\n6. THE MURRAY METHOD <a href=\"http://thewhiskeyscout.com/?page_id=453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthewhiskeyscout.com%2F%3Fpage_id%3D453&d=Jgko0oAfh0uKBKLDRogm5PjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=3df13703\" target=\"_blank\">http://thewhiskeyscout.com/?page_id=453</a><br />\n7. Whisky Q <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/whiskyQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FwhiskyQ%2F&d=Jgko0oAfh0uKBKLDRogm5PjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=020e7fbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/whiskyQ/</a><br />\n8. 威士忌 從零開始 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/startfromzerotowhisky/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstartfromzerotowhisky%2F&d=Jgko0oAfh0uKBKLDRogm5PjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=df8ae8a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/startfromzerotowhisky/</a><br />\n小弟<span style=\"color: red;\">(久米仙巴打)</span>開既Page，自己都係新手慢慢學緊，好明白新手係好需要幫助先入到門，就將自己學既野寫出黎比人睇，循序漸進咁一齊學野，亦都會整合人地既資料同文章去比讀者。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q and A答問大會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q</span>: 新手入門，想識多D又無從入手?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">A</span>: 個人建議幾個方法: <br />\n1.搵朋友痴酒<br />\n一開始唔知自己鍾意飲咩口味既朋友，可以去朋友到痴酒飲下，等朋友Guide住你飲。<br />\n<br />\n2.成本論: 去Whisky Bar 叫1 shot 試酒<br />\n冇朋友咁點算？可以自己去Ginger(Whisky Bar)試Beginner Set，連埋加一都係160$就試到3杯入門級酒，講緊係8-12年左右既貨色。咁樣自然唔洗買完一支先發覺飲完一啖唔岩，要棄成支啦。<br />\n<br />\n3.酒舖試酒<br />\n去酒鋪試酒，好多酒鋪都有開左幾支酒係到比人試，唔洗錢試，如鴻源、億升、the raremalt等。一開始對比唔同風味既酒黎試最好，一杯Sherry風味，一杯泥媒風味，好易就聞到個分別。<br />\n<br />\n當然自己買左幾支係屋企飲既朋友，一定要買一對聞香杯，對比自己既酒黎感受個分別。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q</span>: 新手入門飲邊隻好?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">A</span>: 以下係樓主個人推薦，先試多D唔同風味去搵自己岩飲咩味<br />\n花香: TTL Bourbon(Omar), Glenmorangie Original, Glenfiddich 12, AnCnoc 12, Dalwhinnie 15<br />\n雪莉(Sherry): GlenDronach 12, Macallan 12<br />\n<br />\n要特別d， 可以試下d煙味威，<br />\n海風┼煙燻味: Talisker 10<br />\n<br />\n下面就再重口味小小，有正露丸，醫院味，煙味同碘酒味，一開始唔建議試 第一次試我就建議唔好成支買，搵朋友或者去Bar 小試1shot 係點樣，接唔接受到:<br />\n煙燻泥煤: Lagavulin 16, Ardbeg10, Laphroaig 10<br />\n<br />\n再進階D 追唔同廠既味既話 依個表岩你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tUXnbjd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtUXnbjd.jpg&h=0d4ab74e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q</span>: Single Malt Whisky同Blended Whisky有咩分別?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">A</span>: Single Malt Whisky係指用一間酒廠出產既麥芽威士忌裝入樽既威士忌，並唔係指用同一種麥芽製成既威士忌，代表之一: Macallan 12。Blended Whisky係用唔同酒廠出產既威士忌調合而成，而用於調合既威士忌原材料可以係唔同穀物，如大麥(barley)、裸麥(rye)、小麥(wheat)、玉米(corn)。代表之一: Johnnie Walker"},{"pid":"0aaafd7f8f22cb0c5baec9ab585975acaf6421d6","tid":709116,"uid":22952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T18:25:36.000Z","msg":"有自己買過一枝嚟飲 入嚟學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5437b35881c89ff9484057eee0028ab2a8b46bbd","tid":709116,"uid":61267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T18:43:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/709119/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/709119/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nSOR 開錯區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}